snippet.title: TREASURE TECH, A DOOM GAMEPLAY MOD (RELEASED)
snippet.description:
Play as Treasure Guy as you beat up demons and collect ancient and strange
treasures to make yourself even more powerful! Tackle them! Throw them! Stomp em down! Use a variety of exotic weapons to aid you on your quest for gold, gems, and everything in between!

Download here! You will need GZDOOM, and a Doom1 or Doom2 IWAD to play Treasure Tech! Play it with your favorite map sets that use regular doom monsters!

https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=66995
